title: Attendance taker (Pasalista)

container.value: Transformacion Industrial, 22, Solidaridad Nacional, 07268, CDMX, Mexico

creator: Anacoluto
descriptionHtml:
Pasalista allows you to keep track of attendance and gradings of your school groups.

In addition to taking assistances, you can also keep track of delays, absences and other elements that may be of interest such as: bad behavior, disrespect, lack of homework, books, uniform, among others. Likewise, you can keep track of your students' gradings.

Pasalista also allows you to access the statistics of each and every one of your students within the range of dates you select.

In addition, Pasalista allows you to generate unlimited reports in PDF and CSV format with detailed information on all your students.

With the free version you can generate a maximum of 2 groups. If you want to create more groups, you must purchase the Premium version, which frees your application from all restrictions and eliminates advertising content. This payment is unique and forever.
